            audio="211_03",
            audio_day=0
        },
        {
            talk_id=4207,
            talk_seq=2,
            talker=43186,
            talk_text="祝融贤兄，可否借用你的三昧真火，将这玄冰解开？",
            audio="224_01",
            audio_day=0
        },
        {
            talk_id=4207,
